e>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/posts/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>第一章 道可道，非常道；名可名，非常名。无名天地之始，有名万物之母。故常无欲，以观其妙；常有欲，以观其徼（jiào）。此两者同出而异名，同谓之</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>道德经</category><category>性功</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>道德经-马王堆帛书版</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/posts/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F-%E9%A9%AC%E7%8E%8B%E5%A0%86%E5%B8%9B%E4%B9%A6%E7%89%88/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/posts/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F-%E9%A9%AC%E7%8E%8B%E5%A0%86%E5%B8%9B%E4%B9%A6%E7%89%88/</guid><description>01 道可道也，非恒道也。名可名也，非恒名也。无名万物之始也，有名万物之母也。故：恒无欲也，以观其眇；恒有欲也，以观其徼。两者同出，异名同谓。玄</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>道德经</category><category>性功</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>太上老君说常清静妙经篡图解注王玠</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/posts/%E6%B8%85%E9%9D%99%E7%BB%8F%E5%9B%BE%E8%A7%A3%E6%B3%A8/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 20:06:41 -0500</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 20:06:41 -0500</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/posts/%E6%B8%85%E9%9D%99%E7%BB%8F%E5%9B%BE%E8%A7%A3%E6%B3%A8/</guid><description>版本是元末道士王玠所注解，王玠，字道渊，号混然子。有自述小令《混然歌》： 混然道士何所为，三家村里藏踪迹。 无去无来每独存，无形无名赤厉历。 一点</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>清静经</category><category>性功</category><category>道</category><category>讲经</category></item><item><title>太上老君说常清静经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/posts/%E6%B8%85%E9%9D%99%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 20:06:41 -0500</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 20:06:41 -0500</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/posts/%E6%B8%85%E9%9D%99%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>老君曰：大道无形，生育天地；大道无情，运行日月；大道无名，长养万物；吾不知其名，强名曰道。夫道者：有清有浊，有动有静；天清地浊，天动地静；男</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>清静经</category><category>性功</category><category>早晚课</category><category>炁體源流</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>洞玄灵宝定观经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/posts/%E5%AE%9A%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 20:06:41 -0500</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 20:06:41 -0500</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/posts/%E5%AE%9A%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>诵读 天尊告左玄真人曰：夫欲修道，先能舍事。 外事都绝，无与忤心。然后安坐，内观心起。若觉一念起，须除灭, 务令安静。 其次，虽非的有贪着，浮游乱想</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>定观经</category><category>性功</category><category>早晚课</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>黄帝阴符经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/posts/%E9%BB%84%E5%B8%9D%E9%98%B4%E7%AC%A6%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 20:06:41 -0500</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 20:06:41 -0500</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/posts/%E9%BB%84%E5%B8%9D%E9%98%B4%E7%AC%A6%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>上篇 观天之道，执天之行，尽矣。故天有五贼，见之者昌。五贼在心，施行于天。宇宙在乎手，万化生乎身。天性，人也；人心，机也。立天之道，以定人也。</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>黄帝阴符经</category><category>阴符经</category><category>早晚课</category><category>性功</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item></channel></rss>